FBIS4-37084 "drnes116_j_94001" FBIS-NES-94-116 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Kuwait U.S. Ambassador Uninjured in Road Accident U.S. Ambassador Uninjured in Road Accident LD1406141494 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 1350 GMT 14 Jun 94 LD1406141494 Kuwait KUNA Arabic BFN [Text] Kuwait City, 14 Jun (KUNA) -- The car of Ryan Crocker, U.S. ambassador to Kuwait, was involved in a road accident today. Two persons sustained slight injuries as a result of this accident. A statement released by the U.S. Embassy, a copy of which was received by KUNA, said that "the ambassador was not injured in this accident; while two other persons, one of whom was the ambassador's driver, sustained slight injuries." The statement indicated that the accident happened at 1000 local time at Roundabout No. 2.
